---
name    : detroit-grancher
version : 0.1.0
title   : Detroit Grancher
summary : Grancher plugin for Detroit

description:
  Grancher plugin for Detroit build system uses the grancher
  gem to copy a project's website directory to github gh-pages
  branch and push it the github.com during the publish phase.
  While quite usable, this plugin has been superceded by the
  github gem for most use cases.

resources:
  home: http://detroit.github.com/
  code: http://github.com/detroit/detroit-grancher
  mail: http://groups.google.com/rubyworks-mailinglist

requirements:
  - detroit
  - grancher

authors:
  - T. Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>

